You know, if Psalm 16 was the background track of the Savior, Jesus in his earthly life.

38:46.253 --> 38:52.882
If in reliance upon God, every day Jesus was singing Psalm 16, because you are at my right hand, I shall not be shaken.

38:54.114 --> 38:59.021
Now that Jesus rules in heaven and his spirit's been poured out on the church, Psalm 16 gets to be who?

38:59.823 --> 39:08.556
Our background track, we get to be the ones who say, because you, Jesus, are at God's right hand, we will not be shaken.

39:09.618 --> 39:11.981
We can be unshaken.

39:13.003 --> 39:14.946
Has everything to do with where Jesus is?

39:15.006 --> 39:17.389
If he's on his throne, we can be unshaken.

39:17.670 --> 39:19.933
If God is for us, who can be against us?

39:20.174 --> 39:23.058
If Jesus claims you, who can condemn you?

39:23.650 --> 39:27.154
If Jesus intercedes for you, what can finally defeat you?

39:28.896 --> 39:34.563
That was the spirit that animated the book of Acts from start to finish because of where Jesus is.

39:34.623 --> 39:36.465
Matt can cease to rule the world.

39:37.666 --> 39:38.888
I don't have to be in control.

39:38.908 --> 39:42.612
I don't need to labor under the illusion of control.

39:42.732 --> 39:48.419
Friends, may we live our lives boldly and fearlessly in light of this fact.

39:49.580 --> 39:51.442
Jesus rules.

